
On linux:
1) install nvidia-cuda-toolkit
2) download cuda-samples consistent with you cuda version and copy the Common directory to the project root.
3) make

Then run run.sh.

The command

./bin/sobel_filter.exe

gives the format, and 

./bin/sobel_filter.exe <INPUT_FILE> <OUTPUT_FILE>

where INPUT_FILE is a greyscale 8bit char image is the generic command.

